{"tid":775361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃雨「淋穿」太和, 元朗站 月台現瀑布大堂變水塘","createTime":"2018-08-11T06:07:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T09:58:37.000Z","uid":164771,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9381fca999a0e2b43443f4ad0a79eee1735ccedf","tid":775361,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:07:11.000Z","msg":"醜聞纏身的港鐵竟不敵「黃雨」來襲，今日(11日)至少2個港鐵站出現「室內落雨」情況。有網民今早在社交網站上載影片，東鐵太和站一個月台牆身出現嚴重漏水，疑似由天花板漏出，並形成小型瀑布，雨水傾瀉程度與外間的大雨不相上下，令月台地面出現大攤積水。東網今早亦收到讀者報料，西鐵元朗站大堂亦出現大範圍漏水，地面濕漉漉，港鐵出動近20名職員幫忙拖地，場面墟冚。<br />\n<br />\n網民Siu Yuen今早8時在Facebook群組「Tai Po 大埔」上載影片，太和站的月台地面出現大攤積水，幸好是日周末，否則在繁忙時間大批乘客上落，容易造成「跣倒」等安全問題。另有讀者早上8時許在元朗站拍攝到該站大堂出現大面積漏水，多名港鐵職員忙於拖地清理積水，並用沙包堆放在大堂的商舖門口。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民擔心港鐵室內漏水會引起漏電問題，促港鐵盡快處理，但有網民就批評港鐵車費年年加，醜聞及管理不善等問題卻日日新鮮；有網民更暗諷港鐵「周圍火頭」，無暇理會漏水等小事。東網正向港鐵查詢漏水事宜，暫未獲回覆。"},{"pid":"72bac54ac670fc6a845f796e69e7f3a1182b7bfa","tid":775361,"uid":112583,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:09:36.000Z","msg":"因鐵"},{"pid":"b777c3c3917ff2bc787a5901c656f6ad41c347dd","tid":775361,"uid":47080,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:12:59.000Z","msg":"醜鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抵死過因航，收皮啦"},{"pid":"b6a517f495a5c6b1598b4bf5dae532f9c96d24b0","tid":775361,"uid":15823,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:14:00.000Z","msg":"黃雨唔係咁簡單架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今鋪大交合vs狗鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3398285fb286e6c77bb4f0a4bc491e0d324d711","tid":775361,"uid":76310,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:19:10.000Z","msg":"世紀一遇既黃雨"},{"pid":"8ceecd193fac1e9a99e8a67b841eece1a0e0443e","tid":775361,"uid":35914,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:19:22.000Z","msg":"因大雨而導致上蓋漏水的港鐵"},{"pid":"df775e78ba0ecf8f76890d596b7143e80221fc99","tid":775361,"uid":23829,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:20:49.000Z","msg":"太和終於出人頭地了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係住呢頭都唔為意有呢個站存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146d4139cf4a4e37699a9f1bfcfdc0f9bb52a852","tid":775361,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"太和個站不嬲露天<br />\n只係裝左隔音屏<br />\nif 紅磡, 旺角漏水就離譜d"},{"pid":"6858a2c3e4d4e42dc853f3d4ab56d247414fe74c","tid":775361,"uid":80072,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:42:22.000Z","msg":"醜事爆唔停 到底馬狗呢隻太監做過咩嚟"},{"pid":"a59d4c13131f039794ad8456058a91c69f0ca921","tid":775361,"uid":2923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6858a2c3e4d4e42dc853f3d4ab56d247414fe74c","tid":775361,"uid":80072,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:42:22.000Z","msg":"醜事爆唔停 到底馬狗呢隻太監做過咩嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:46:40.000Z","msg":"收花紅收到手軟,唔得閒搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e9c41c89a1731fcfbef9564f750e20f6a37f05","tid":775361,"uid":54733,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/26144643/image1527317171380.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F26144643%2Fimage1527317171380.png&h=340db408&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec997141503804abac90fcb41d0f5e560a341994","tid":775361,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:51:40.000Z","msg":"加價囉"},{"pid":"4601c3eaa412fec2c398c2807b44b108a39a49dd","tid":775361,"uid":887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:53:25.000Z","msg":"開個post冇片冇相都算<br />\n你連link都咖擺出嚟"},{"pid":"dd4f3561b61532d7f917af590c8886c5b58ecfc9","tid":775361,"uid":22047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re